playing this weakening move? --- ANSWER: Black must deal with the threat of
e4-e5 and the pressure on the d7-pawn.} ({Alternatives are: a)} 12... O-O {
is not good enough as the threat of e4-e5 is too strong. After} 13. e5 g6 14.
Qh3 Nh5 15. Bh6 Ng7 16. Rxd7 (16. Nc3 {retaining the idea of taking on d7 is
