{and White's attempt to give checkmate falls just short, for example} 20. g4 ({
or} 20. Bf6 Qc6) 20... Rae8 21. gxh5 Rxe5 22. Nd2 f6 23. Bh4 Rxh5 24. Qf4 g5 {
