I don't like the look of this for Black. Open h-file, the e4-rook is short of
squares... --- ANSWER: As Benoni players will know, there are dynamic features
to counter these other potential 'issues'. The open h-file is not enough in
itself to give checkmate, and as for the rook on e4, he has his own ideas...}
