though technical difficulties remain.} 30. Nc3 Bc4 31. Bf1 Kf7 32. b3 Bxf1 33.
Kxf1 g5 {Those extra pawns will come in handy, and they begin to roll down the
board.} 34. Ra2 g4 35. Rh2 Kg6 36. Rh8 f4 37. Re8 Kf7 38. Rb8 f3 39. Rxb6 {
