nice Hedgehog structure and will look to play ...b5 or ...d5 at the opportune
time.}) 7... bxc5 (7... Bxc5 {is completely fine too, and the choice between
the two options is a matter of taste.}) 8. Bg5 Be7 9. e3 O-O {Both sides now
quietly complete their development.} 10. Be2 d6 11. Qc2 Nbd7 12. O-O Qb6 {
Andrei Sokolov is very well versed in the arts of the Queen's Indian
structures, and with simple play he gets a very nice position. At the right
moment, he will play ...d5 and end up with a favourable hanging pawns
structure after c4xd5 and ...e6xd5. More on that later in the game...} 13. b4
h6 (13... cxb4 14. axb4 Qxb4 $2 15. Rab1 {, winning the b7-bishop, was the
