(28. Nxd4 $2 exd4 {and now the e4-pawn needs protecting.}) 28... Rb6 29. Qxa5
Qb7 30. Qd2 f6 {The human move, to defend the g5-pawn and prevent the white
queen getting in.} (30... Bxe4 {was playable, but needed to be calculated.
